hbouring%20country...%20Pakistan...%20needs%20to%20be%20blamed%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20was%20quoted%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fnoida%2Fncr-air-quality-hits-very-poor-levels-officials-blame-pakistans-stubble-burning%2Farticleshow%2F114664309.cms%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Times%20of%20India%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%C2%A0%26quot%3BIncreasing%20instances%20of%20stubble%20burning%20has%20sent%20toxic%20smoke%20across%20the%20border.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Gupta's%20remark%20came%20after%20the%20AQI%20in%20the%20three%20cities%20dropped%20to%20'very%20poor'%20levels%20Sunday%3B%20Noida%20recorded%20an%20AQI%20of%20304%20(on%20a%20scale%20of%20500)%2C%20a%20deeply%20worrying%20spike%20from%20169%20a%20day%20earlier.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGhaziabad%20reported%20a%20similarly%20worrying%20AQI%20-%20324%20-%20and%20Greater%20Noida%20312.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20AQI%20in%20Delhi%20was%20even%20worse%20-%20an%20average%20of%20352%20was%20recorded%20Sunday%2C%20with%20the%20Anand%20Vihar%20area%20reporting%20a%20reading%20of%20405%20as%20a%20layer%20of%20acrid%20and%20lung-burning%20smog%20covered%20the%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20morning%20the%20AQI%20in%20Noida%2C%20Greater%20Noida%2C%20and%20Ghaziabad%20dropped%20to%20267%2C%20248%2C%20and%20252%2C%20with%20Delhi%20reporting%20an%20overall%20reading%20of%20328%20and%20'very%20poor'%20air%20quality%20levels.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20lack%20of%20winds%20had%20compounded%20the%20problem%20-%20there%20was%2C%20literally%2C%20no%20breeze%20in%20parts%20of%20the%20city%20Sunday%2C%20according%20to%20the%20India%20Meteorological%20Department%20-%20trapping%20pollutants%20in%20the%20air.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConcerns%20over%20air%20quality%20-%20and%20the%20consequent%20spike%20in%20respiratory%20illnesses%20-%20have%20become%20a%20perennial%20problem%20for%20Delhi%20and%20neighbouring%20regions%3B%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20last%20week%20grilled%20the%20central%2