Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Fpotop55o_c285-aircraft_625x300_28_October_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%20Narendra%20Modi%20came%20to%20power%20at%20the%20Centre%20with%20a%20majority%20of%20his%20own%20in%202014%2C%20he%20launched%20the%20ambitious%20%26quot%3BMake%20in%20India%26quot%3B%20initiative%2C%20placing%20it%20in%20mission%20mode.%20The%20crux%20of%20this%20push%20was%20his%20strong%20belief%20that%20a%20country%20as%20large%20as%20India%20cannot%20leap%20forward%20without%20its%20own%20manufacturing%20capabilities%20and%20must%20not%20rely%20solely%20on%20imports%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20emerging%20global%20scenario.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%26quot%3BMake%20in%20India%26quot%3B%20initiative%20was%20intertwined%20with%20the%20%26quot%3BAtmanirbhar%20Bharat%26quot%3B%20(Self-reliant%20India)%20motto.%20Modi's%20political%20rivals%20and%20habitual%20critics%20mocked%20him%2C%20not%20only%20because%20they%20were%20unwilling%20to%20come%20to%20terms%20with%20this%20new%20reality%20but%20also%20because%20they%20had%20never%20truly%20understood%20the%20potential%20of%20a%20new%20and%20rising%20India.%20They%20even%20joked%20about%20the%20%26quot%3BMake%20in%20India%26quot%3B%20lion%20logo.%20For%20them%2C%20Modi's%20vision%20of%20aggressively%20promoting%20the%20domestic%20defence%20equipment%20and%20armaments%20sector%2C%20along%20with%20entering%20the%20export%20market%2C%20seemed%20even%20more%20unworkable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELittle%20did%20they%20realise%20that%20Modi%2C%20with%20his%20untiring%20energy%20and%20forward%20vision%2C%20had%20become%20the%20guiding%20light%20of%20an%20aspirational%20India%2C%20internalising%20the%20mantra%20to%20%26quot%3Bthink%20big%2C%20dream%20big%26quot%3B.%20The%20government's%20orientation%20underwent%20a%20swift%20transformation%2C%20marking%20a%20clear%20divide%20between%20pre-2014%20and%20post-2014%20thought%20processes%20and%20actions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20October%2028%2C%20the%20%26quot%3BMake%20in%20India%26quot%3B%20lion%20roared%20loudly.%20This%20date%20is%20historically%20significant%20for%20India's%20defence%20sector%20as%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20Spanish%20Prime%20Minister%20Pedro%20Sanchez%20jointly%20inaugurated%20India's%20first%20private%20facility%20to%20manufacture%20military%20aircraft%E2%80%94the%20Tata-Airbus%20C295%20project%20in%20Vadodara.%20This%20marks%20the%20first%20instance%20of%20a%20military%20aircraft%20being%20manufactured%20by%20a%20private%20company%20on%20Indian%20soil%20and%20symbolises%20a%20significant%20leap%20forward%20in%20India's%20self-reliance%20in%20defence.%20The%20project%20is%20structured%20to%20ensure%20that%20every%20step%20of%20the%20aircraft's%20creation%20is%20anchored%20in%20India%2C%20with%20over%2018%2C000%20homegrown%20parts%20contributing%20to%20the%20endeavour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20the%20total%2056%20C-295%20aircraft%20designated%20for%20the%20Indian%20Air%20Force%2C%2016%20will%20be%20delivered%20directly%20by%20Airbus%20from%20Spain%2C%20while%20the%20remaining%2040%20will%20be%20manufactured%20locally%20under%20this%20joint%20collaboration.%20The%20first%20of%20these%2040%20aircraft%20is%20expected%20to%20roll%20out%20in%202026%2C%20with%20deliveries%20scheduled%20to%20be%20completed%20by%202031%2C%20replacing%20the%20Indian%20Air%20Force's%20legacy%20Avro%20aircraft.%20The%20C-295%20will%20be%20utilised%20for%20the%20tactical%20transport%20of%20soldiers%20and%20paratroopers%20to%20locations%20inaccessible%20to%20current%20heavier%20aircraft.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20drive%20behind%20manufacturing%20defence%20equipment%20and%20armaments%20in%20India%2C%20along%20with%20the%20associated%20budgetary%20and%20policy%20support%2C%20stems%20from%20the%20belief%20that%20a%20robust%2C%20self-reliant%20security%20infrastructure%20is%20crucial%20for%20a%20nation's%20economic%20prosperity%20and%20sustainability.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConsider%20these%20facts%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIn%202019%2C%20the%20Stockholm%20International%20Peace%20Research%20Institute%20(SIPRI)%20ranked%20India%20among%20the%20top%2025%20arms%20exporters%20worldwide%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20placing%20the%20country%20at%2023rd%20position.%20India%20aims%20to%20achieve%20defence%20exports%20of%20%E2%82%B935%2C000%20crore%20by%202025.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20percentage%20of%20defence%20spending%20on%20foreign%20procurement%20dropped%20from%2046%25%20in%202018-19%20to%2036.7%25%20by%20December%202022%2C%20showcasing%20the%20country's%20commitment%20to%20self-reliance.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIndia's%20defence%20exports%20surged%20from%20%E2%82%B9686%20crore%20in%202013-14%20to%20an%20impressive%20%E2%82%B921%2C083%20crore%20in%202023-24%2C%20with%20the%20scope%20of%20exports%20now%20extending%20to%20over%20100%20countries%2C%20underscoring%20the%20quality%20and%20reliability%20of%20Indian-made%20military%20products.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIndia's%20defence%20budget%20has%20seen%20substantial%20growth%2C%20rising%20from%20%E2%82%B92.03%20lakh%20crore%20in%202013-14%20to%20%E2%82%B95.93%20lakh%20crore%20in%202023-24.%20This%20investment%20is%20aimed%20at%20modernising%20defence%20infrastructure%20and%20has%20contributed%20to%20India%20achieving%20its%20highest-ever%20defence%20production%20output%20of%20%E2%82%B91.27%20lakh%20crore%20in%202023-24%2C%20up%20from%20%E2%82%B940%2C000%20crore%20in%202013-14.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ETwo%20major%20defence%20industrial%20corridors%20have%20been%20established%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20and%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20attracting%20investments%20of%20%E2%82%B97%2C000%20crore%20to%20create%20an%20ecosystem%20that%20supports%20indigenous%20defence%20production.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIn%202024%2C%20%E2%82%B91%2C500%20crore%20has%20been%20allocated%20to%20support%20startups%20and%20MSMEs%20within%20the%20defence%20procurement%20budget%2C%20signalling%20the%20government's%20intent%20to%20nurture%20homegrown%20innovations.%20Approximately%208%2C000%20MSMEs%20currently%20operate%20in%20the%20defence%20sector%2C%20with%20a%20goal%20to%20double%20this%20number%20in%20the%20coming%20years.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20Innovations%20for%20Defence%20Excellence%20(iDEX)%20initiative%20has%20emerged%20as%20a%20game-changer%2C%20with%20over%20400%20startups%20and%20MSMEs%20participating%20to%20provide%20innovative%20solutions.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20inauguration%20of%20the%20Tata%20Aircraft%20Complex%20for%20C-295%20aircraft%20production%20reflects%20how%20a%20rising%20nation's%20dreams%20can%20become%20a%20reality%20with%20strong%20political%20will%20and%20the%20necessary%20policy%20push.%20From%20building%20Asia's%20largest%20helicopter%20facility%20to%20nurturing%20local%20startups%20and%20manufacturing%20advanced%20naval%20platforms%2C%20India's%20defence%20sector%20has%20rapidly%20embodied%20a%20self-sustained%20model%20of%20growth%20and%20capability.%20While%20there%20is%20still%20much%20work%20to%20be%20done%2C%20it%20has%20made%20a%20strong%20start.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(The%20author%20Consulting%20Editor%2C%20NDTV)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1730107380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Fpotop55o_c285-aircraft_625x300_28_October_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fgujarats-c-295-facility-reflects-a-rising-nations-dreams-6891602%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20inauguration%20of%20the%20Tata%20Aircraft%20Complex%20for%20C-295%20aircraft%20production%20reflects%20how%20a%20rising%20nations%20dreams%20can%20become%20a%20reality%20with%20strong%20political%20will%20and%20the%20necessary%20policy%20push.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%2