0a%20rally%20he%20reportedly%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BYou%20are%2030%20per%20cent%20(of%20the%20people%20here)%20but%20we%20are%2070%20per%20cent...%20if%20you%20think%20you%20can%20demolish%20mosques%20and%20Muslims%20will%20sit%20back%20and%20relax...%20(you%20are%20wrong).%20I%20will%20leave%20politics%20if%20I%20don't%20drown%20you%20people%20in%20the%20Bhagirathi...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3BShoot%20Me...%20Let's%20See%20How%20Many%20Bullets%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20actor%20-%20speaking%20at%20a%20membership%20drive%20-%20then%20called%20on%20BJP%20supporters%20to%20join%20the%20party's%20karyakartas.%20%26quot%3BWe%20want%20those%20people%20who%20will%20fight...%20who%20can%20stand%20up%20and%20say%2C%20'Shoot%20me...%20let%20me%20see%20how%20many%20bullets%20you%20have'%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20taking%20a%20swipe%20at%20the%20Trinamool%20over%20multiple%20incidents%20of%20pre-%20and%20post-poll%20violence%20in%20the%20state%2C%20%26quot%3BBut%20we%20don't%20want%20those%20who%20join%20for%20money.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChakraborty%20then%20also%20offered%20up%20a%20second%20violent%20threat.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20cut%20down%20one%20fruit%20from%20our%20trees...%20we%20will%20cut%20down%20four%20of%20yours%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20as%20Mr%20Shah%20continued%20to%20look%20on%20impassively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3BNo%20One%20Takes%20Him%20Seriously...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Trinamool%20hit%20back%20swiftly%3B%20party%20General%20Secretary%20Jay%20Prakash%20Majumdar%20was%20quoted%20by%20a%20national%20news%20channel%20as%20dismissing%20Chakraborty%20as%20an%20inconsequential%20figure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNo%20one%20takes%20him%20seriously%20as%20a%20political%20leader...%20the%20leader%20(the%20Trinamool's%20Kabir)%20whose%20comment%20he%20spoke%20about%20was%20censured%20(by%20the%20Election%20Commission).%20But%20now%2C%20in%20the%20p