%22%3A%22She%20Locked%20Boyfriend%20Inside%20Suitcase%20In%20Hide-And-Seek%2C%20Went%20To%20Sleep.%20He%20Died%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20Florida%20woman%20has%20been%20convicted%20of%20second-degree%20murder%20following%20a%202020%20incident%20in%20which%20she%20zipped%20her%20boyfriend%20into%20a%20suitcase%20causing%20his%20death.%20The%20jury%20reached%20the%20verdict%20on%20October%2025%20after%20a%20trial%20revealed%20the%20circumstances%20surrounding%20the%20case.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnSarah%20Boone%2C%20now%2047%2C%20said%20her%20boyfriend%2C%2042-year-old%20Jorge%20Torres%20Jr%2C%20was%20trapped%20in%20the%20suitcase%20during%20a%20hide-and-seek%20game.%20The%20couple%20had%20been%20drinking%20wine%20and%20working%20on%20puzzles%20in%20their%20apartment.%20According%20to%20an%20arrest%20affidavit%20from%20the%20Orange%20County%20Sheriff's%20Office%2C%20the%20couple%20believed%20it%20would%20be%20%E2%80%9Cfunny%E2%80%9D%20to%20fit%20inside%20the%20suitcase%20as%20part%20of%20their%20game%2C%20reported%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%2Cnoindex%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2024%2F10%2F26%2Fus%2Fflorida-woman-boyfriend-suitcase-guilty-murder%2Findex.html%5C%22%3ECNN%3C%2Fa%3E.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnWhen%20Boone%20zipped%20Torres%20into%20the%20blue%20suitcase%2C%20she%20noticed%20two%20of%20his%20fingers%20protruding%20from%20the%20opening%20and%20assumed%20he%20would%20free%20himself.%20After%20zipping%20him%20inside%2C%20she%20went%20to%20bed%2C%20expecting%20him%20to%20join%20her.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnUpon%20waking%2C%20Boone%20found%20Torres%20unresponsive%20inside%20the%20suitcase%20and%20immediately%20called%20911.%20When%20deputies%20from%20the%20Orange%20County%20Sheriff's%20Office%20arrived%2C%20they%20discovered%20Torres%20lying%20near%20the%20front%20door%20of%20the%20residence%2C%20next%20to%20the%20blue%20suitcase.%20Boone%20initially%20said%20she%20did%20not%20believe%20he%20was%20trapped%20inside%20when%20she%20left%20him%20there.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnA%20release%20from%20the%20attorney's%20office%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CEvidence%20presented%20during%20the%20trial%20included%20videos%20found%20on%20Boone's%20phone%20where%20Torres%20could%20be%20heard%20frantically%20pleading%20to%20be%20released%20while%20Boone%20laughed%20and%20rebuffed%20him%20several%20times.%20In%20the%20videos%20she%20recorded%2C%20the%20victim%20could%20be%20heard%20telling%20the%20defendant%20he%20could%20not%20breathe%20and%20asking%20to%20be%20let%20out%20of%20the%20suitcase.%20Boone%20responded%20with%2C%20%E2%80%98That's%20what%20you%20get.%20%E2%80%98That's%20what%20I%20feel%20like%20when%20you%20cheat%20on%20me%2C'%20and%20other%20taunts.%E2%80%9D%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnDuring%20the%20trial%2C%20Boone%20took%20the%20stand%20in%20her%20own%20defence%2C%20saying%20she%20had%20no%20intention%20of%20killing%20Torres.%20She%20claimed%20her%20actions%20were%20in%20self-defence%2C%20alleging%20Torres%20previously%20abused%20her%20and%20insisting%20she%20did%20not%20mean%20to%20cause%20him%20harm.%20But%20her%20testimony%20was%20undermined%20by%20her%20earlier%20statements%20and%20video%20evidence%20that%20showed%20her%20mocking%20the%20victim%20as%20he%20pleaded%20to%20be%20freed%20from%20the%20suitcase.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnAfter%20a%2010-day%20trial%2C%20the%20jury%20found%20Boone%20guilty%20of%20second-degree%20murder.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnDescribing%20her%20reaction%2C%20Boone's%20attorney%20told%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%2Cnoindex%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wesh.com%2Farticle%2Fsarah-boone-trial-verdict-guilty%2F62716043%5C%22%3EWESH%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20an%20affiliate%20of%20CNN%2C%20%E2%80%9CJust%20shock.%20She's%20shocked%2C%20you%20know.%20She%20felt%20like%2C%20you%20know%2C%20she%20had%20a%20defence%2C%20as%20you%20know.%20We're%20obviously%20very%20disappointed.%E2%80%9D%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnFor%20Torres's%20family%20members%2C%20the%20verdict%20provided%20some%20sense%20of%20closure%2C%20said%20state%20attorneys.%20%E2%80%9CI%20think%20they%20were%20finally%20just%20happy%20to%20see%20this%20case%20go%20to%20trial%20and%20be%20able%20to%20put%20this%20one%20in%20the%20books%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20an%20attorney.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnBoone%20is%20set%20to%20receive%20her%20sentence%20on%20December%202%2C%20according%20to%20the%20statement%20from%20the%20attorney's%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1730106960000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2F9efd1378_sarah-boone_625x300_28_October_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-woman-guilty-of-killing-boyfriend-after-zipping-him-in-a-suitcase-during-hide-and-seek-game-6890288%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sarah%20Boone%20said%20her%20boyfriend%20got%20trapped%20in%20the%20suitcase%20during%20a%20hide-and-seek%20game.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-woman-guilty-of-killing-boyfriend-after-zipping-him-in-a-suitcase-during-hide-and-seek-game-6890288%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20'Diwali%20gift'%20scam%20message%20on%20WhatsApp%20cost%20Bengaluru%20techie%20Rs%204.5%20Lakh%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1730106415000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-114687186%2Cimgsize-39338.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Ftechnology%2Ftech-news%2Fhow-diwali-gift-scam-message-on-whatsapp-cost-bengaluru-techie-rs-4-5-lakh%2Farticleshow%2F114687186.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20Bengaluru%20techie%20lost%20Rs%204.5%20lakh%20in%20a%20gift%20card%20scam%20after%20receiving%20a%20fraudulent%20WhatsApp%20message%2C%20seemingly%20from%20his%20boss.%20He%20bought%20and%20shared%20Apple%20voucher%20codes%2C%20later%20discovering%20the%20scam%20through%20HR.%20An%20FIR%20was%20filed%2C%20and%20police%20have%20begun%20inves