0haven't%20yet%20signed%20up%20for%20new%20subscriptions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20some%20customers%20are%20charged%20this%20fee%20if%20they%20initially%20dropped%20support%20but%20then%20resumed%20it%20when%20they%20upgraded%20to%20a%20new%20version.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTwo%20customers%20I%20was%20talking%20to%20last%20week%20said%2C%20'Out%20of%20nowhere%2C%20it%20seems%2C%20a%20VMware%20sales%20rep%20sent%20me%20a%20note%20and%20said%2C%20hey%2C%20if%20they%20don't%20renew%20before%20SnS%20expires%2C%20there%20will%20be%20a%2020%25%20late%20renewal%20fee%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Dean%20Colpitts%2C%20CTO%20at%20Members%20IT%20Group.%20%26quot%3BMy%20response%20was%2C%20how%20can%20there%20be%20a%20late%20renewal%20fee%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELikewise%2C%20Ignacio%20Llorente%2C%20CEO%20of%20OpenNebula%20Systems%2C%20said%20in%20an%20email%20that%20his%20company%20has%20received%20%26quot%3Bnumerous%20emails%20from%20companies%20expressing%20concerns%20over%20VMware's%20recent%20changes%20in%20contractual%20terms%2C%20licensing%20models%2C%20and%20pricing%20policies.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMany%20customers%20who%20transitioned%20from%20perpetual%20licenses%20to%20VMware's%20subscription-based%20services%20are%20finding%20the%20new%20model%20challenging%2C%20as%20they%20are%20unaccustomed%20to%20the%20ongoing%20renewal%20process%2C%26quot%3B%20Llorente%20said.%26quot%3B%20This%20has%20led%20to%20some%20being%20caught%20off%20guard%20by%20unexpected%20additional%20costs%2C%20especially%20when%20renewals%20are%20missed.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EColpitts%20said%20that%20the%20text%20about%20the%20late%20fee%20in%20the%20email%20was%20bolded%2C%20making%20it%20seem%20like%20a%20%26quot%3Bscare%20tactic.%26quot%3B%20He%20added%20that%20customers%20did%20not%20get%20any%20previous%20warnings%20or%20communication%20about%20this%20late%20fee.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey're%20not%20giving%20customers%20any%20disc