%20in%20a%20dead%20heat%20in%20the%20polls%2C%20Americans%20are%20in%20suspense%20about%20how%20their%20lives%20will%20change%20under%20a%20new%20leader.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20has%20prepared%20a%20five-part%20refresher%20for%20the%20final%20stretch%20that%20will%20unpack%20the%20potential%20impact%20that%20both%20Donald%20Trump%20and%20Kamala%20Harris%20presidencies%20will%20have%20on%20US%20consumers.%20Today's%20first%20installment%20is%20focused%20on%20the%20investment%20landscape.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20date%2C%20Trump%20and%20Harris%20have%20outlined%20specific%20policy%20proposals%20that%20will%20impact%20different%20parts%20of%20the%20stock%20market.%20Their%20varying%20platforms%20will%20also%20be%20crucial%20in%20determining%20the%20future%20path%20of%20interest%20rates%2C%20which%20will%20shape%20the%20bond%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20they're%20not%20expected%20to%20have%20diametrically%20opposed%20impacts%20on%20everything%2C%20with%20both%20candidates%20seen%20as%20positive%20forces%20for%20crypto.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDetailed%20below%20is%20the%20latest%20research%20and%20commentary%20from%20top%20Wall%20Street%20strategists%2C%20outlining%20how%20the%20market%20and%20investing%20landscape%20will%20shift%20under%20potential%20Trump%20or%20Harris%20administrations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20guide%20covers%20four%20specific%20asset%20classes%2C%20and%20is%20divided%20between%20the%20Trump%20and%20Harris%20impact%20on%20each.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2240896f3b-9c3a-42aa-82ae-49a1761381ac%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Stocks%5C%22%3EStocks%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20the%20perspective%20of%20equities%2C%20it's%20helpful%20to%20look%20at%20the%20potential%20impact%20on%20both%20the%20micro%20(specific%20sectors%20set%20to%20be%20impacted)%20and%20the%20macro%20(how%20the%20broader%20market%20will%20respond).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2224c47698-0ee7-4a48-bb04-abe2a4f630c2%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ETrump%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Ch4%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2251cc4655-bf14-43bc-b772-b54703215a1c%5C%22%3ESectors%3C%2Fh4%3E%3Cp%3EMuch%20of%20the%20industry%20guidance%20for%20the%20stock%20market%20under%20Trump%20boils%20down%20to%20his%20proposed%20tax%20policies.%20Bank%20of%20America%20says%20his%20plan%20to%20cut%20the%20corporate%20tax%20rate%20to%2015%25%20from%2021%25%20will%20boost%20corporate%20earnings%20by%204%25.%20How%20much%20it%20impacts%20each%20sector%20ultimately%20depends%20on%20sensitivity%20to%20changes%20in%20the%20tax%20rate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20that%20end%2C%20BofA%20says%20the%20consumer%20discretionary%20and%20communication%20services%20sectors%20%E2%80%94%20the%20areas%20most%20beholden%20to%20tax-rate%20changes%20%E2%80%94%20will%20benefit%20the%20most.%20On%20the%20flip%20side%2C%20less%20exposed%20areas%20like%20utilities%2C%20real%20estate%2C%20and%20energy%20will%20get%20the%20smallest%20boost.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20energy%20specifically%2C%20Trump's%20pro-drilling%20stance%20%E2%80%94%20while%20supportive%20of%20industry%20activity%20%E2%80%94%20will%20likely%20lead%20to%20oversupply%20and%20lower%20oil%20prices%2C%20says%20BNY%20Wealth.%20That%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20will%20hurt%20corporate%20profitability%20in%20the%20sector%20and%20drag%20on%20stock%20prices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20also%20worth%20noting%20that%20energy%20was%20the%20worst-performing%20sector%20during%20Trump's%20previous%20presidential%20tenure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFinancials%20is%20another%20area%20of%20the%20stock%20market%20seen%20benefiting%20from%20a%20Trump%20win.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fmarkets%2Fus%2Fif-trump-wins-he-plans-free-wall-street-burdensome-regulations-2024-04-12%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EAllies%20of%20the%20former%20president%20have%20said%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20he%20aims%20to%20unburden%20banks%20from%20many%20of%20the%20regulations%20that%20were%20imposed%20following%20the%202008%20financial%20crisis%2C%20something%20that%20his%20first%20administration%20tried%20to%20do%20with%20limited%20success.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThose%20looser%20regulations%20could%20could%20also%20ignite%20a%20fresh%20wave%20of%20mergers%20and%20acquisitions%2C%20which%20would%20increase%20advisory%20revenue%20for%20big%20banks%20and%20help%20drive%20up%20profits%20from%20dealmaking.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch4%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2208ac2f7c-0094-48df-8910-ca3b12ae746a%5C%22%3EBroader%20market%3C%2Fh4%3E%3Cp%3EZooming%20out%20and%20assessing%20the%20full%20equity-market%20landscape%2C%20views%20are%20divided%2C%20particularly%20along%20partisan%20lines.%20Trump's%20proposed%20tax%20and%20regulatory%20policies%20are%20seen%20by%20his%20supporters%20as%20pro-business%2C%20which%20would%20be%20good%20news%20for%20corporate%20profit%20growth%20and%20deal%20activity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Trump%20critics%20argue%20that%20his%20proposal%20for%20universal%20tariffs%20and%20steeper%20levies%20on%20Chinese%20imports%20%E2%80%94%20as%20well%20as%20a%20crackdown%20on%20immigration%20%E2%80%94%20will%20be%20inflationary%2C%20which%20could%20hold%20back%20stock%20prices.%20The%20nonpartisan%20Tax%20Foundation%20says%20the%20tariff%20plan%20in%20particular%20could%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftaxfoundation.org%2Fblog%2Ftrump-mckinley-tariffs-great-depression%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehurt%20profit%20margins%20and%20put%20pressure%20on%20consumer%20spending%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBank%20of%20America%20estimates%20that%2060%25%20tariffs%20on%20China%20and%2010%25%20on%20other%20countries%20would%20lower%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20earnings%20per%20share%20by%203.1%25.%20That%20would%20be%20a%20problem%20since%20earnings%20growth%20has%20long%20been%20the%20stock%20market's%20primary%20driver%20of%20gains.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20conventional%20wisdom%20is%20wrong%3A%20Trump%20is%20not%20going%20to%20substantially%20cut%20taxes%20once%20in%20office%3B%20he%20is%20going%20to%20raise%20taxes%20by%20jacking%20up%20