ion%20lip%20gloss%20shade%20called%20%26quot%3BMajor%20Flex.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENetflix%20has%20also%20collaborated%20on%20other%20projects%20for%20some%20of%20its%20hit%20shows.%20In%20May%2C%20it%20launched%20a%20partnership%20with%20the%20cosmetics%20company%20Lush%20for%20its%20hit%20period%20romance%20series%20%26quot%3BBridgerton.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2217376f7e-814f-48c0-841b-3a5658c9cb85%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EGaming%20moves%20into%20the%20mainstream%20%E2%80%94%20and%20brings%20in%20a%20lot%20of%20eyeballs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20season%20of%20%26quot%3BArcane%26quot%3B%20was%20released%20in%202021.%20It%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnetflixs-league-of-legends-series-arcane-surges-in-popularity-2021-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etopped%20Netflix's%20charts%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20the%20No.%201%20English-language%20series%20globally%20from%20November%2015%20to%20November%2021%20of%20that%20year%2C%20with%20viewers%20watching%2038.4%20million%20hours%20of%20the%20show%20that%20week%2C%20according%20to%20the%20streamer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20season%20is%20set%20to%20drop%20in%20three%20parts%20on%20November%209%2C%2016%2C%20and%2023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BArcane%26quot%3B%20is%20but%20one%20of%20Netflix's%20recent%20gaming-related%20content%20offerings.%20In%202022%2C%20the%20platform%20released%20a%20live-action%20show%20based%20on%20the%20hit%20game%20franchise%20Resident%20Evil.%20It's%20also%20invested%20in%20animated%20shows%2C%20like%20the%202023%20breakout%20show%20%26quot%3BBlue%20Eye%20Samurai.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOutside%20of%20Netflix%2C%20gaming%20is%20solidly%20in%20the%20spotlight%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20nerdworld%20business%20is%20thriving.%20%26quot%3BLeague%20of%20Legends%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20game%20on%20which%20%26quot%3BArcane%26quot%3B%20is%20based%2C%20is%20in%20the%20final%20stages%20of%20its%202024%20World%20Championship.%3C%2Fp%3E%