e-se-4-to-feature-a18-chip-8gb-ram-for-apple-intelligence-report-124102800398_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22When%20Shark%20Tank's%20Jane%20Lu%20Received%20The%20%26quot%3BWorst%20Job%20Application%20Ever%26quot%3B%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EJane%20Lu%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20online%20fashion%20retailer%20Showpo%2C%20has%20shared%20the%20%26quot%3Bworst%20job%20application%20ever%26quot%3B%20she%20received.%20The%20application%2C%20to%20assist%20her%2C%20appears%20to%20have%20been%20written%20with%20artificial%20intelligence%20(AI)%2C%20the%20Australian%20businesswoman%20said.%20She%20discovered%20blatant%20errors%20and%20likened%20it%20to%20%E2%80%9CChatGPT%20copy%20and%20paste.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnypost.com%2F2024%2F10%2F27%2Flifestyle%2Fceo-slams-embarrassing-gen-z-job-application-trend%2F%5C%22%3Evideo%20on%20TikTok%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Ms%20Lu%2C%20a%20panellist%20on%20Shark%20Tank%2C%20read%20out%20the%20application%2C%20highlighting%20the%20lack%20of%20attention%20to%20various%20details%20in%20it.%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20confident%20that%20my%20experience%20in%20(relevant%20experience%2Fskill)%20positions%20me%20as%20a%20strong%20candidate%2C%E2%80%9D%20read%20the%20job%20application.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnIn%20the%20document%2C%20key%20details%20such%20as%20the%20skills%20on%20%E2%80%9Cspecific%20projects%2C%20courses%20or%20initiatives%E2%80%9D%20were%20left%20blank%2C%20indicating%20how%20the%20applicant%20failed%20to%20proofread%20it%20before%20submitting%20it%20to%20the%20company.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20applicant%20did%20not%20remove%20part%20of%20the%20prompt%20generated%20by%20the%20AI%20platform%20at%20the%20top%20of%20the%20cover%20letter%2C%20which%20read%2C%20%E2%80%9CHere%20is%20a%20more%20polished%20and%20articulate%20version%20of%20your%20cover%20letter%E2%80%9D.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnLu%20noted%20that%20the%20applicant%20%26quot%3Bcopied%20and