2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bishnoi%20Gang's%20Rival%20Fires%20At%20Delhi%20Businessman's%20House%2C%20Leaves%20A%20Note%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ETwo%20men%20affiliated%20with%20the%20Bambiha%20Gang%2C%20the%20rival%20of%20the%20incarcerated%20gangster%20Lawrence%20Bishnoi%2C%20opened%20fire%20at%20the%20residence%20of%20a%20businessman%20in%20Delhi%2C%20police%20said%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20shooting%20occurred%20in%20North%20West%20Delhi's%20Rani%20Bagh%20around%208.40%20am%20on%20Saturday%20and%20the%20two%20accused%2C%20who%20were%20on%20a%20bike%2C%20threw%20a%20chit%20on%20which%20'Bambiha%20Gang'%20was%20written.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20least%20six%20to%20seven%20rounds%20were%20fired%20outside%20the%20house%2C%20officials%20said.%20However%2C%20no%20call%20has%20so%20far%20been%20received%20regarding%20extortion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelhi%20has%20witnessed%20an%20increase%20in%20firing%20incidents%20as%20part%20of%20extortion%20attempts%20recently.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20month%2C%20three%20sensational%20incidents%20of%20firing%20occurred%20in%20the%20capital%20--%20at%20a%20car%20showroom%20in%20Naraina%20in%20west%20Delhi%2C%20a%20hotel%20in%20southwest%20Delhi%20and%20the%20sweet%20shop%2C%20all%20were%20linked%20to%20extortion%20activities%20by%20gangsters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20first%20incident%2C%20shots%20were%20fired%20at%20a%20second-hand%20car%20showroom%20called%20'Car%20Street%20Mini'%20in%20southwest%20Delhi's%20Naraina%2C%20barely%20a%20kilometre%20from%20the%20Naraina%20police%20station.%20Officials%20said%20at%20least%2020%20rounds%20were%20fired%20by%20three%20men%20who%20entered%20the%20showroom%2C%20causing%20panic%20in%20the%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20shooters%20left%20behind%20a%20slip%2C%20reading%20%26quot%3BBhau%20Gang%2C%20Since%202020%26quot%3B.%20The%20%26quot%3BBhau%20Gang%26quot%3B%20mention%20was%20seen%20as%20a%20reference%20to%20wanted%20gangster%20Himanshu%20Bhau%2C%20who%20fled%20the%20country%20in%202022%20and%20is%20currently%20believed%20to%20be%20in%20Portugal.%20He%20had%20also%20claimed%20responsibility%20for%20the%20murder%20of%20a%20man%20at%20a%20food%20outlet%20in%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20May%2C%20a%20similar%20shooting%20was%20carried%20out%20at%20a%20car%20showroom%20in%20West%20Delhi's%20Tilak%20Nagar%20and%20the%20same%20gang%20was%20suspected%20to%20be%20behind%20the%20attack.%20Sources%20Rs%205%20crore%20was%20demanded%20from%20the%20owners%20of%20the%20'Fusion%20Cars'%20showroom.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20shooting%20took%20place%20in%20southwest%20Delhi's%20Mahipalpur%20when%20a%20bike-borne%20shooter%20fired%20at%20least%205-6%20rounds%20at%20the%20Hotel%20Impress%20and%20damaged%20its%20glass%20gate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20sources%2C%20the%20firing%20was%20done%20to%20extort%20money%20and%20take%20over%20the%20hotel.%20Last%20year%2C%20a%20man%20had%20threatened%20the%20hotel%20owner%20in%20the%20name%20of%20Canada-based%20gangster%20Goldie%20Brar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBrar%2C%20along%20with%20gangster%20Lawrence%20Bishnoi%2C%20who%20is%20currently%20lodged%20in%20a%20jail%20in%20Gujarat%2C%20are%20also%20accused%20of%20carrying%20out%20a%20shooting%20outside%20the%20Mumbai%20residence%20of%20Bollywood%20actor%20Salman%20Khan%20earlier%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20third%20incident%20took%20place%20in%20west%20Delhi's%20Nangloi%20where%20bullets%20were%20fired%20at%20a%20sweet%20shop.%20The%20police%20found%20a%20slip%20with%20the%20name%20of%20jailed%20gangster%20Deepak%20Boxer.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1730098500000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2F9ne8jc6g_delhi-firing_625x300_28_October_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Flawrence-bishnoi-gangs-rival-bambiha-gang-fires-at-delhi-businessmans-house-leaves-a-note-6890569%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20shooting%20occurred