tly%20inaugurated%20the%20TATA%20Aircraft%20Complex%20for%20manufacturing%20the%20C-295%20aircraft%20in%20Vadodara%2C%20the%20first%20private%20sector%20final%20assembly%20line%20for%20military%20aircraft%20in%20India.%20A%20total%20of%2040%20military%20tactical%20transport%20aircraft%20will%20be%20built%20at%20the%20Vadodara%20facility%20as%20part%20of%20the%20agreement%2C%20while%20aviation%20giant%20Airbus%20will%20deliver%2016%20aircraft%20directly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAbout%20C-295%20aircraft%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20C-295%20is%20a%20transport%20aircraft%20of%205-10%20tonne%20capacity%20with%20contemporary%20technology%20that%20will%20replace%20the%20Indian%20Air%20Force's%20ageing%20Avro-748%20planes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20C-295%20is%20known%20to%20be%20a%20superior%20aircraft%20used%20for%20tactical%20transport%20of%20up%20to%2071%20troops%20or%2050%20paratroopers%20and%20for%20logistic%20operations%20to%20locations%20that%20are%20not%20accessible%20to%20current%20heavier%20aircraft.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20aircraft%20can%20cruise%20at%20the%20speed%20of%20260%20knots%20and%20can%20also%20operate%20on%20short%20airstrips.%20It%20can%20also%20land%20successfully%20on%20unpaved%2C%20soft%2C%20and%20sandy%2Fgrass%20airstrips.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20aircraft%2C%20called%20%26quot%3Brobust%20and%20reliable%26quot%3B%2C%20with%20a%20flight%20endurance%20of%20up%20to%2011%20hours%2C%20can%20carry%20out%20multi-role%20operations%20under%20all%20weather%20conditions.%20It%20can%20routinely%20operate%20day%20as%20well%20as%20night%20combat%20missions%20from%20desert%20to%20maritime%20environments%2C%20apart%20from%20disaster%20response.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20can%20serve%20as%20a%20flying%20ICU%2C%20equipped%20for%20medical%20evacuations.%20It%20is%20equipped%20for%20the%20air-to-air%20refueling%20of%20fixed-wing%20aircraft%20and%20helicopters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20C-295%20has%20a%20rear%20ramp%20door%20for%20quick%20reaction%20and%20para-dropping%20of%20troops%20and%20cargo.%20Short%20take-off%2Fland%20from%20semi-prepared%20surfaces%20is%20another%20of%20its%20features.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%2056%20aircraft%20under%20the%20agreement%20will%20also%20be%20fitted%20with%20an%20indigenous%20Electronic%20Warfare%20suite%20manufactured%20by%20Indian%20DPSUs%20-%20Bharat%20Electronics%20Ltd%20and%20Bharat%20Dynamics%20Limited.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFitted%20with%20a%20retractable%20landing%20gear%20and%20featuring%20an%20unobstructed%2012.69-meter-long%20pressurized%20cabin%2C%20the%20C295%20cruises%20at%20altitudes%20up%20to%2030%2C000%20feet%2C%20while%20also%20retaining%20excellent%20low-level%20flight%20characteristics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20C295%20is%20combat%20proven%2C%20having%20been%20successfully%20used%20during%20long%20deployments%20in%20remote%20areas%20such%20as%20Chad%2C%20Iraq%20and%20Afghanistan.%20It%20routinely%20operates%20in%20the%20hot%20and%20humid%20conditions%20of%20the%20Brazilian%20jungle%20and%20Colombian%20mountains%2C%20in%20the%20dusty%20and%20very%20hot%20deserts%20of%20Egypt%20and%20Algeria%2C%20and%20in%20the%20extremely%20cold%20and%20icy%20winters%20of%20Poland%2C%20Finland%20and%20Kazakhstan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAbout%20the%20Tata%20Aircraft%20Complex%20in%20Vadodara%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20facility%2C%20operations%20will%20involve%20the%20full%20development%20of%20a%20complete%20ecosystem%2C%20from%20manufacture%20to%20assembly%2C%20test%20and%20qualification%2C%20to%20delivery%20and%20maintenance%20of%20the%20complete%20life%20cycle%20of%20the%20aircraft.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20C-295%20aircraft%20may%20come%20out%20of%20Tata-Airbus'%20factory%20in%20Vadodara%20in%20September%202026.%20The%20remaining%2039%20aircraft%20are%20to%20be%20delivered%20by%20August%202031.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20the%20Tatas%2C%20leading%20defence%20public%20sector%20units%2C%20such%20as%20Bharat%20Electronics%20and%20Bharat%20Dynamics%2C%20as%20well%20as%20private%20micro%2C%20small%20and%20medium%20enterprises%20will%20contribute%20to%20this%20programme.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20will%20be%20largest%20operator%20of%20the%20aircraft%20with%2056%20units%20by%202031.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1730097780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Fpotop55o_c285-aircraft_625x300_28_October_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fall-weather-multi-functional-all-about-the-c-295-military-aircraft-6890501%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20his%20Spanish%20counterpart%20Pedro%20Sanchez%20jointly%20inaugurated%20the%20TATA%20Aircraft%20Complex%20for%20manufacturing%20the%20C-295%20aircraft%20in%20Vadodara.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fall-weather-multi-functional-all-about-the-c-295-military-aircraft-6890501%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20Gary%20Kirsten%20Quit%20As%20Pakistan's%20Coach%3F%20Real%20Reason%20Revealed%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPakistan's%20white-ball%20coach%20Gary%20Kirsten%20has%20decided%20to%20step%20down%20after%20developing%20a%20rift%20with%20the%20country's%20cricket%20board%20within%20six%20months%20of%20being%20appointed%2C%20according%20to%20multiple%20reports.%20The%2056-year-old%2C%20who%20coached%20India%20to%20victory%20at%20the%202011%20ODI%20World%20Cup%2C%20was%20appointed%20by%20the%20PCB%20(Pakistan%20Cricket%20Board)%20in%20April%20end%20this%20year.%20It%20has%20been%20reported%20that%20cracks%20started%20to%20develop%20between%20Kirsten%20and%20the%20Pakistan%20Cricket%20Board%20ever%20since%20the%20national%20selection%20committee%20was%20given%20the%20sole%20responsibility%20of%20picking%20teams%2C%20with%20no%20input%20from%20the%20coach%20or%20the%20captain%20being%20taken.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPakistan's