0Pakistan's%20white-ball%20tour%20of%20Australia%20starting%20November%204.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20team%20is%20riding%20high%20on%20a%20come-from-behind%202-1%20triumph%20over%20visiting%20England%20in%20a%20Test%20series%20that%20concluded%20last%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3EWith%20PTI%20Inputs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1730097720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2F8tt39gdo_gary-kirsten-twitter_625x300_09_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fexplained-why-gary-kirsten-quit-as-pakistans-white-ball-coach-6890216%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20per%20the%20report%2C%20his%20decision%20to%20quit%20is%20down%20to%20a%20rift%20with%20red%20ball%20coach%20Jason%20Gillespie%2C%20and%20the%20PCB%20after%20the%20board%20decided%20to%20withdraw%20their%20selection%20powers.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A58%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fexplained-why-gary-kirsten-quit-as-pakistans-white-ball-coach-6890216%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Prince%20William%20Shares%20How%20Diana's%20Compassion%20Led%20Him%20To%20Tackle%20Homelessness%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPrince%20William%20has%20opened%20up%20about%20how%20a%20childhood%20experience%20with%20his%20late%20mother%2C%20Princess%20Diana%2C%20influenced%20him%20to%20help%20the%20homeless.%C2%A0In%20his%20upcoming%20documentary%2C%3Cem%3E%20Prince%20William%3A%20We%20Can%20End%20Homelessness%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20the%2042-year-old%20recalls%20his%20first%20visit%20to%20'The%20Passage'%2C%20a%20London%20charity%20dedicated%20to%20helping%20homeless%20people.%20Accompanied%20by%20his%20brother%2C%20Prince%20Harry%2C%20and%20Diana%2C%20William%20first%20visited%20the%20organisation%20when%20he%20was%2011.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20mother%20took%20me%20to%20The%20Passage%3B%20she%20took%20Harry%20and%20I%20both%20there%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20Prince%20of%20Wales%20recalled%20in%20a%20newly%20released%20clip%20from%20the%20two-part%20series%2C%20as%20per%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%2Cnoindex%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2024%2F10%2F27%2Fuk%2Fprince-william-diana-photos-homelessness-intl%2Findex.html%5C%22%3ECNN%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9CI'd%20never%20been%20to%20anything%20like%20that%20before%2C%20and%20I%20was%20a%20bit%20anxious%20as%20to%20what%20to%20expect.%E2%80%9D%20His%20mother%20lightened%20the%20mood%2C%20%E2%80%9Chaving%20a%20laugh%20and%20joking%20with%20everyone%2C%E2%80%9D%20putting%20him%20at%20ease%2C%20the%20Royal%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20visit%20had%20a%20profound%20impact%20on%20Prince%20William.%20%E2%80%9CI%20remember%20thinking%2C%20'Well%2C%20if%20everyone's%20not%20got%20a%20home%2C%20they're%20all%20going%20to%20be%20really%20sad.'%20But%20it%20was%20incredible%20how%20happy%20an%20environment%20it%20was...%20That's%20when%20it%20dawned%20on%20me%20that%20there%20are%20other%20people%20out%20there%20who%20don't%20have%20the%20same%20life%20as%20you%20do.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20documentary%2C%20directed%20by%20BAFTA%20winner%20Leo%20Burley%2C%20chronicles%20the%20Prince's%20Homewards%20initiative%20%E2%80%94%20a%20five-year%20project%20launched%20in%20June%202023%20aimed%20at%20ending%20homelessness%20in%20six%20flagship%20locations%20across%20the%20UK.%20It%20also%20highlights%20the%20stories%20of%20individuals%20experiencing%20homelessness%20or%20struggling%20with%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHomelessness%20is%20%E2%80%9Ca%20complex%20societal%20issue%E2%80%9D%2C%20he%20stressed%2C%20but%20added%20it%20can%20be%20eradicated.%20%E2%80%9CAchieving%20this%20will%20require%20a%20movement%20that%20creates%20systemic%20change.%20A%20change%20that%20focuses%20on%20prevention%20rather%20than%20management.%20And%20one%20that%20ensures%20all%20young%20people%20have%20truly%20affordable%20options%20to%20live%20and%20thrive%20independently.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20documentary%20also%20addresses%20criticisms%20over%20the%20Prince's%20privileged%20background%20and%20whether%20he%20is%20suited%20to%20tackle%20such%20issues.%20In%20another%20clip%2C%20he%20responded%20that%20he%20had%20%E2%80%9Cno%20other%20agenda%20than%20desperately%20trying%20to%20help%20people%E2%80%9D%20who%20are%20in%20need.%20%E2%80%9CI%20see%20that%20as%20part%20of%20my%20role.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20documentary%20will%20premiere%20on%20ITV%20at%202%3A30%20am%20IST%20on%20Thursday%2C%20October%2031.%20The%20second%20episode%20will%20air%20at%20the%20same%20time%20the%20following%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1730097660000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2F9lq14feg_princess-diana-prince-william-reuters_625x300_28_October_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fprince-william-shares-how-dianas-compassion-led-him-to-tackle-homelessness-6890461%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Prince%20William%20has%20opened%20up%20about%20how%20a%20childhood%20experience%20with%20his%20late%20mother%2C%20Princess%20Diana%2C%20influenced%20him%20to%20help%20the%20homeless.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fprince-william-shares-how-dianas-compassion-led-him-to-tackle-homelessness-6890461%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'What%20are%20you%20doing%20with%20Ruturaj%20Gaikwad%3F'%3A%20Cricket%20legend%20to%20selectors%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1730097463000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-114680940%2Cimgsize-23800.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fnews%2Fwhat-are-you-doing-with-ruturaj-gaikwad-cricket-legend-hits-out-at-selectors-over-border-gavaskar-snub%2Farticleshow%2F114680587.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22