20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F671ed44d9b3250dbbcea6ef1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222200%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EElon%20Musk%20on%20Sunday%20gave%20a%20brief%20speech%20at%20a%20campaign%20rally%20for%20Donald%20Trump%20in%20New%20York.%3Cp%3EANGELA%20WEISS%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EElon%20Musk%20briefly%20spoke%20at%20a%20campaign%20rally%20for%20Donald%20Trump%20in%20New%20York%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EMusk%20said%20he'd%20save%20the%20US%20%242%20trillion%20through%20a%20department%20of%20government%20efficiency.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EMusk%20did%20not%20provide%20any%20details%20on%20policy%20changes%20or%20spending%20cuts%20he'd%20implement.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20campaign%20rally%20for%20former%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20in%20New%20York%20on%20Sunday%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EElon%20Musk%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20he'd%20save%20the%20United%20States%20%242%20trillion%20through%20a%20department%20of%20government%20efficiency.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHoward%20Lutnick%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20the%20financial-services%20company%20Cantor%20Fitzgerald%2C%20introduced%20Musk%20at%20the%20event.%20As%20he%20took%20the%20stage%2C%20Lutnick%20asked%20the%20Tesla%20and%20SpaceX%20CEO%2C%20%26quot%3BHow%20much%20do%20you%20think%20we%20can%20rip%20out%20of%20this%20wasted%20%246.5%20trillion%20Harris-Biden%20budget%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20we%20can%20do%20at%20least%20%242%20trillion%2C%26quot%3B%20Musk%20replied.%20%26quot%3BI%20mean%2C%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%2C%20you're%20being%20taxed.%20You're%20being%20taxed.%20All%20government%20spending%20is%20taxation.%20So%20whether%20it's%20direct%20taxation%20or%20all%20government%20spending%2C%20it%20either%20becomes%20inflation%20or%20it's%20direct%20taxation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BYour