0that%20neither%20Trump%20nor%20Harris%20has%20proposed%20a%20plan%20that%20would%20fix%20Social%20Security's%20finances%20but%20that%20Trump's%20proposals%20would%20%26quot%3Bdramatically%20worsen%20Social%20Security's%20finances.%26quot%3B%20Trump's%20campaign%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-presidency-would-make-things-worse-for-social-security-nonprofit-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehas%20disputed%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20findings%20of%20the%20CRFB's%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%20organized%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Fpolitics%2Felections%2Feconomists-say-inflation-deficits-will-be-higher-under-trump-than-harris-0365588e%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esurvey%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%2050%20economists%20from%20October%204%20to%20October%208%20and%20found%20that%2065%25%20said%20the%20deficit%20would%20get%20worse%20with%20the%20policies%20Trump%20has%20proposed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b8347404-0b41-4b1f-ae6f-f08ec695d7a9%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EMusk's%20growing%20support%20for%20Trump%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%2C%20the%20world's%20richest%20person%2C%20has%20become%20one%20of%20Trump's%20staunchest%20and%20most%20vocal%20backers%20in%20this%20election%20cycle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-donald-trump-feud-relationship-timeline-2022-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eendorsed%20Trump%20in%20July%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20the%20former%20president%20survived%20an%20assassination%20attempt%20during%20a%20rally%20in%20Pennsylvania.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20have%20discussed%20Musk%20holding%20a%20seat%20in%20Trump's%20Cabinet%20if%20the%20former%20president%20were%20to%20be%20reelected.%20During%20a%20livestream%20on%20X%20in%20August%2C%20Musk%20said%20he%20would%20be%20%26quot%3Bhappy%20to%20help%20out%26quot%3B%20with%20a%20government-efficiency%20commission.%20In%20a%20September%20spee