2%80%99s%20beloved%20chef%20%E2%80%94%20takes%20a%20few%20seconds%20to%20unmute%20his%20mic%20and%20adjust%20his%20camera%2C%20giving%20me%20a%20clear%20view%20of%20him%20in%20his%20elegant%20New%20York%20City%20home%2C%20I%20can%E2%80%99t%20help%20but%20smile%20at%20this%20%E2%80%98pinch-me%E2%80%99%20moment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERight%20from%20the%20outset%2C%20Khanna%20is%20chipper%3B%20no%20one%20(except%20probably%20the%20general%20manager%20at%20%E2%80%98Bungalow%E2%80%99%2C%20Sameer%20Bhatt)%20would%20guess%20he%20has%20pulled%20an%20all-nighter.%20Well%20into%20the%20wee%20hours%20of%20the%20morning%2C%20Khanna%20was%20attempting%20to%20replicate%20the%20intricate%20wings%20of%20a%20peacock%E2%80%99s%20feathers%20onto%20the%20surface%20of%20a%20piece%20of%20coconut%20%3Cem%3Ebarfi%3C%2Fem%3E%20(Indian%20sweet).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%222400846096%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFour%20decades%20of%20culinary%20experience%20ensured%20he%20aced%20the%20task.%20And%20now%20for%20replicating%20the%20same%20onto%20a%20hundred-odd%20pieces!%20Known%20to%20push%20the%20envelope%2C%20Khanna%20does%20justice%20to%20this%20reputation%20when%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20wanted%20each%20feather%20to%20be%20exactly%20alike.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharing%20how%20the%20plumage%20was%20meant%20to%20be%20reminiscent%20of%20the%20%3Cem%3Emandirs%20%3C%2Fem%3E(temples)%20in%20Indian%20homes%2C%20Khanna%20was%20keen%20that%20every%20guest%20at%20%E2%80%98Bungalow%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%20his%20dream%20restaurant%20project%20launched%20in%20New%20York%20in%20March%20this%20year%20%E2%80%94%20return%20home%20that%20day%20with%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F288997%2Fpunjabi-wrestler-harbans-